OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and often cloudy morning,
OL,6,Fwith a few brighter spells, cloud
OL,7,Fclearing in the afternoon to give
OL,8,Flonger sunny periods. Light winds but
OL,9,Fbreezy along the coast. Very mild.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FClear skies to start but some
OL,12,Flow cloud in the west and north later
OL,13,Fand fog patches forming overnight
OL,14,Fmainly in the south. Remaining
OL,15,Frelatively mild.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FEarly fog clearing, then
OL,18,Fdry and very mild with warm sunny
OL,19,Fspells during Wednesday. Winds slowly
OL,20,Fease throughout the day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
